                  <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed" style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed); color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
                    My name is <strong class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Ramizbhai Pinjara</strong>, and I am a passionate <strong class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Full Stack Developer</strong> with <strong class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">4+ years</strong> of experience. My specialization lies in building fast, user-friendly, and <strong class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">SEO-optimized</strong> web applications. I take projects from concept to final delivery, ensuring clean and scalable engineering throughout the process.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <!-- Right Side: Image -->
                <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 flex items-center justify-center" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                  <img
                    src="/about.png"
                    srcset="/about.png 600w, /about.png 1200w"
                    sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 70vw, 600px"
                    alt="Ramizbhai Pinjara - Full Stack Developer with 4+ years of experience in web development"
                    class="h-auto rounded-xl object-cover"
                    style="border-radius: var(--radius-lg); max-width: 70%; height: auto; width: 70%;"
                    loading="lazy"
                    decoding="async"
                    width="600"
                    height="400"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Technical Expertise -->
              <div>
