                        <td class="p-4 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed" style="padding: var(--spacing-2); font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed); color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
                          I design smooth and modern UIs using React.js, <strong class="text-blue-400">Next.js</strong>, Tailwind CSS, and shadcn/ui. I bring rich and engaging interactions to life with Framer Motion.
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td class="p-4 font-semibold text-slate-300" style="padding: var(--spacing-2); font-size: var(--font-size-base); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold); color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Full Stack & Back-End</td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed" style="padding: var(--spacing-2); font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed); color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
                          I possess strong Full Stack skills in JavaScript, <strong class="text-blue-400">TypeScript</strong>, Node.js, and Express. For databases, I work with MongoDB and <strong class="text-blue-400">MySQL</strong>, allowing me to build fully functional applications.
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Work Philosophy -->
              <div>
                <h2 class="font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400" style="font-size: var(--font-size-h3); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-2);">
                  <span>ðŸš€</span>
                  <span>Work Philosophy</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4" style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed); color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);">
                  I also work as a freelancer, helping clients deliver <strong class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">high-performance and impactful digital products</strong>.
                </p>
                <ul class="list-none space-y-3" style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--spacing-2);">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold flex-shrink-0" style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg);">â€¢</span>
