                      <strong class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Readiness:</strong> I am always ready for new ideas, complex tasks, or any challenging project thrown my way.
                    </span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold flex-shrink-0" style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg);">â€¢</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed" style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed); color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
                      <strong class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Eagerness to Learn:</strong> I am constantly eager to learn, experiment, and grow professionally, and excited to collaborate on meaningful products.
                    </span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- Current Experimentation -->
              <div>
                <h2 class="font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400" style="font-size: var(--font-size-h3); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-2);">
                  <span>ðŸ’¡</span>
                  <span>Current Experimentation</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed" style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed); color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
                  I am currently building my own <strong class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Smart Home Automation</strong> project. Through this, I am experimenting with modern technologies to create intelligent and connected systems.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- Personal Interests -->
              <div>
                <h2 class="font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400" style="font-size: var(--font-size-h3); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-2);">
                  <span>â˜•</span>
                  <span>Personal Interests</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4" style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed); color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);">
                  When I'm not coding, I pursue activities that help me relax and refresh my mind:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-none space-y-3" style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--spacing-2);">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold flex-shrink-0" style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg);">â€¢</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed" style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed); color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
